---
title: Monterey Jack Chicken Sandwich with Balsamic Onions and Potato Wedges
description: Somewhere along the line, sandwiches were deemed “lunch food only,” and we’re here to call that bad marketing. Sandwiches could not be more dinner-worthy, people! Our chefs have officially reclaimed the handheld meal and now present it to you in its most hearty, delicious, and satisfying form. Pan-seared chicken breast is served under a blanket of gooey Monterey Jack, tangy balsamic caramelized onions, and a creamy sauce. There’s even a side of roasted potatoes for good measure. Step aside, lunch police!
